Class SelfMonitoringProcessAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unitn.lifecoach.service.process.selfmonitoring.adapter.SelfMonitoringProcessAdapter

  • public class SelfMonitoringProcessAdapter
extends Object
    This class is used as an adapter for self monitoring process centric service. It calls all services related to UserProcessResource, MeasureProcessResource and MeasureFeedbackProcessResource
    Author:
    Elvis Koci , Kemele Muhammed Endris
